      • doHandleError

        protected void doHandleError()
                      throws PageNotFoundException,
                             IOException,
                             PortalException,
                             PageCacheControllerHtml.PageUnavailableException,
                             InterruptedException
        Contains the logic for processing the not found (404) error event.
        Throws:
        PageNotFoundException - if the requested page was not found.
        IOException - if an IO error occurred while writing to the output.
        PageCacheControllerHtml.PageUnavailableException - if the requested page is currently unavailable.
        InterruptedException - if the thread was interrupted.
        PortalException
        Since:
        5.0.0
